#Format for script
#Outputs .eps files at 4k res at 600 dpi
#Number of output files will be the same as no of betas

./opm.sh <potential.py> <Element> <Energy> <Template.inp> <plotter.py>


potential.py - python program that solve for potential

Element - Element name with mass number ex Ca40, Fe54

Template.inp - template file used

plotter.py - python program that plots data from ecis file


For batch run use multi.py

python3 multi.py <batch file>

batch file example-
Ca40 17.3
C12 24.1
Cd112 20.0
end

